# AND Studio generates REAL output only — there is no built-in mock/demo engine.
# Image generation needs a Google Gemini key and presentations need an Anthropic
# key; both are entered by the user in the browser via Settings (this is a
# static, backend-less app), so they are NOT configured here.
#
# The VITE_* keys below are optional and only wire the additional Magnific / Flux
# adapter seams (see build spec §5). They are not required to run the app. Copy
# this file to `.env` and fill one in to activate that provider.

# VITE_MAGNIFIC_KEY=
# VITE_FLUX_KEY=
